name: move up (vell)
description:
move up:
a platfrormer muiltyplayer game where you move fast before your friend go over you 

you win when you go to the last point first!, you lose when you fall!

controls:

player1:    SAD = move,    G or W = jump

player2:    arrows = move,     enter or up = jump

player3:    KJL = move,  space or I = jump
